  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Function <math alttext=\"f\"><mi>f</mi>\n</math> is a quadratic function where <math alttext=\"f left parenthesis negative 20 right parenthesis equals 0\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math> and&nbsp;<math alttext=\"f left parenthesis negative 4 right parenthesis equals 0\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>. The graph of&nbsp;<math alttext=\"y equals f left parenthesis x right parenthesis\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></math> in the <em>xy</em>-plane has a vertex at&nbsp;<math alttext=\"left parenthesis r comma negative 64 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mi>r</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>64</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>. What is the value of <math alttext=\"r\"><mi>r</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
